Gerald Ronson’s Heron Near London Building Purchase, Times Says

-- B y   D a v i d   A l t a n e r
-- 
2011-03-20T10:38:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-20/gerald-ronson-s-heron-near-london-building-purchase-times-says.html
Gerald Ronson’s Heron International
is close to buying the former headquarters of Bass Plc in the
Marylebone area of  London  for 63 million pounds ($102.3
million), the  Sunday Times  said, without saying where it got the
information.  Heron may convert the building into luxury apartments, the
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
David Altaner in London at 
 daltaner@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge in London at 
 Ckeatinge@bloomberg.net  